the life forms that
could be living

00:22:12.590 --> 00:22:14.930 align:middle line:84%
on the Red Planet
at this moment.

00:22:14.930 --> 00:22:18.110 align:middle line:84%
The extremophile
organisms that thrive

00:22:18.110 --> 00:22:21.650 align:middle line:84%
in extreme conditions that
have been found on the Earth

00:22:21.650 --> 00:22:25.520 align:middle line:84%
show that they are very
resistant to practically,

00:22:25.520 --> 00:22:28.340 align:middle line:84%
all of the most difficult
conditions for life.

